{"tid":1075434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11個月大兒子誤墮滾水全身8成燙傷　媽媽痛心︰我不能原諒自己","createTime":"2019-03-24T06:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T16:23:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"707a001c83508b4c4122b11c184d2c1aba44dc26","tid":1075434,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"家居意外防不勝防，即使父母只是離開嬰幼兒一陣子，期間已足以發生事故。烏克蘭一位媽媽準備為11個月大的兒子沖涼，怎知在離開的瞬間，兒子不慎墮進滾水桶，以致全身8成燙傷，生命危在旦夕。<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報道，來自烏克蘭敖德薩州的媽媽Tetyana Chernenko，日前預備洗澡水為11個月大兒子Daniil Chernenko洗澡，她先將一桶滾水放在睡房靠近桌子的地上，再打算去取凍水，以便調節洗澡水的溫度。<br />\n怎知她轉身離開數秒之際，原本在桌上玩耍的Daniil不慎墮入滾水桶中。媽媽發現後，即時把兒子從滾水中拉起來。<br />\n&quot;我抱起他，然後為他裹上毛巾，當我打開毛巾時，卻發現他的皮膚嚴重燙傷而脫皮。&quot;<br />\nDaniil被送往當地醫院，醫生證實他全身8成皮膚燙傷，只有前額、手指及腳趾沒有燙傷。醫生正努力為他搶救，不過認為他的生存機會渺茫。<br />\n從當地義工拍到的照片可見，Daniil躺在病床上，全身包著白色的繃帶，只露出眼睛、鼻子、嘴巴、手掌及腳掌，樣子看來相當痛苦。<br />\n媽媽對兒子的情況表示痛心，她接受當地傳媒訪問時表示︰<br />\n&quot;我不能原諒自己所做的事。&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2305000/2305017/hurt_thumb_20190323_S_V2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2305000%2F2305017%2Fhurt_thumb_20190323_S_V2_1024.jpg&h=47fbdbe4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e22702e07bcfd7e9e3d132dcd86410e7e15e3d8b","tid":1075434,"uid":113626,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"呢d係香港坐硬監 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d3b4aa087cca6dc6892ac01c131feb200bdb53","tid":1075434,"uid":76705,"like":10,"dislike":12,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:01:49.000Z","msg":"Natural selection<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049941efe2b29e3dfa87e077712f2e8af1b57659","tid":1075434,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"98d3b4aa087cca6dc6892ac01c131feb200bdb53","tid":1075434,"uid":76705,"like":10,"dislike":12,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:01:49.000Z","msg":"Natural selection<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adcc94c61b912c96e18702254d5059951bdf74dc","tid":1075434,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e22702e07bcfd7e9e3d132dcd86410e7e15e3d8b","tid":1075434,"uid":113626,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"呢d係香港坐硬監 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2647bd5ee57f7f0ff70deb32e0c03f108e7377","tid":1075434,"uid":133412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:48:05.000Z","msg":"即刻降溫"},{"pid":"0c018e70451b169b56528b96bac1308c6a9f19df","tid":1075434,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:49:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5699316605ade6f66689cde8b56cbf72157e3512","tid":1075434,"uid":97451,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:50:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb63a18c1827afafd4f7afccee15f9e63db7ea6d","tid":1075434,"uid":24857,"like":28,"dislike":5,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"這個小孩比同齡的早熟欸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ac85983cc2aea37f02f30167123c59b9f42414","tid":1075434,"uid":2839,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"bb63a18c1827afafd4f7afccee15f9e63db7ea6d","tid":1075434,"uid":24857,"like":28,"dislike":5,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"這個小孩比同齡的早熟欸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:57:18.000Z","msg":"屌, 你落硬地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmo